title: Hotel Hell ( Season 2 ) [2014]
description:
Hotel Hell ( Season 2 ) Complete x8

Hotel Hell is an American reality television series created, hosted and narrated by Gordon Ramsay that premiered on the Fox network on August 13, 2012. It is Ramsay's fourth series for the Fox network and airs on Monday nights at 8 pm ET/PT. The series' first season, which consisted of six episodes, ended on September 3, 2012. On August 31, 2012, Fox renewed Hotel Hell for a second season (eight episodes), which premiered on July 21, 2014
